        </p>
        <p>
          Future versions may be offered under different terms, including versions
          with paid features. This Agreement does not commit us to distributing any
          future version free of charge.
        </p>

        <h3>13. Distribution through the Microsoft Store</h3>
        <p>
          Where you obtained the Software from the Microsoft Store, Microsoft's
