          Microsoft's terms. This Agreement governs the Software as between you and
          us. Where the two conflict, whichever grants you the broader right prevails.
        </p>

        <h3>14. Entire agreement and severability</h3>
        <p>
          This Agreement, together with
          <code>THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.txt</code>, is the entire agreement between you
          and us concerning the Software, and supersedes any prior statement or
