        </p>

        <h2 id="third-party">Open-source components</h2>
        <p>
          The app is built on Magick.NET and ImageMagick, and ships a number of
          open-source libraries. The complete notice, including the full text of
          every licence and the written offer of source code for the LGPL
          components, is published as a single file:
        </p>
        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/third-party-notices.txt">
            Read the full third-party notices
          </a>
        </p>
        <p>
          A summary, for reviewers who need the component inventory rather than the
          licence texts:
